    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_01-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、お疲れ様です\n……何を見ているんですか？",
      "startTime": 3.4333333254,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2000.0000079000001,
          "startTime": 5.4333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "結婚式場のパンフレットだよ。今度お世話になるから\nどんな場所か調べておこうと思ってね",
      "startTime": 9.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_01-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんが結婚式場のお世話に！？\nあ、あの……それは誰と……",
      "startTime": 15.211481921,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "誰って、一緒に行く相手は怜に決まってるじゃないか",
      "startTime": 18.4405448197,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_01-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "そうなんですね、相手は私……私！？\nこ、これって、もしかして……プロポーズ……！？",
      "startTime": 28.788633148,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_01-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "ちょ、ちょっと待って下さい\n急に言われても心の準備が……",
      "startTime": 35.4219664813,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "どうした？　なんだか様子が変だぞ\n怜は……嫌なのか？",
      "startTime": 41.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_01-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "嫌というか、突然のことで混乱してしまって……\n{user}さんと、け、けけ、結婚……",
      "startTime": 49.3404101929,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "そうか、怜が嫌なら仕方ない……\n分かった、この仕事は俺の方から断っておくよ",
      "startTime": 57.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_01-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "そんなこと、いきなり言われても困りま……\nえ？　今、仕事って言いました？",
      "startTime": 64.7131168288,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}